author: Erin Schumaker
title: The month coronavirus changed America
description: At the beginning of of the month, the nation’s attention was focused on Super Tuesday. Less than 30 days later, the election had been all but forgotten.
content:
COVID-19's breakneck progression in the United States last month was nothing short of historic.
